      "[Benchmark] Fast Sorts on 10,000 records...\n",
      "  Merge Sort  : 0.0204s  | O(n log n) |  Production Ready\n",
      "  Quick Sort  : 0.0155s  | O(n log n) |  Production Ready\n",
