      "[Lookup Engine] Searching for Fraudulent TXN ID: 727293\n",
      "-------------------------------------------------------\n",
      "  Linear Search (unsorted): found at index 8445 | Time: 0.000365s | O(n)\n",
      "  Binary Search (sorted)  : found at index 7000 | Time: 0.000043s | O(log n)\n",
